Popsical app has a refreshed look and we fixed the pairing issue! Important to read In order to make sure the pairing works with this app version you also need to update the Popsical device app version. Once you turn on the Popsical device you will be prompted to update the app to version 2.7.7 . Make sure you complete the download and installation entirely. Alternatively on your TV you can go to settings and select Check for Updates . What s New We have implemented new technology to fix the pairing issue Updated app interface to make your browsing experience better Improved search feature that will show you both artist and track result in one page Simple hold and drag feature to edit the Play Queue

Hey Rockstar! We re always listening to you to provide you with the ultimate karaoke experience with Popsical. This update includes the new features below and some minor fixes for improved performance. 1. My playlist: Save your go to Karaoke songs to your very own custom playlists. Simply go to your My Playlists page and press Create new playlist . 2.
